CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 28, 1953, pg. 16 reads: "A Birds-Eye View Of The Throng...Just a few of the hundreds of friends who crowded the Hotel Sheraton Ballroom Monday night at Mrs. Vann's testimonial birthday party. Approximately 600 persons attended the affair to do honor to the Courier's publisher."
TitMainTitle: Group of women and men wearing evening attire, seated in ballroom of the Hotel Sheraton with sunburst patterned curtains, for Jessie Vann's birthday party
